OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBright but rather cloudy, most
OL,6,Fplaces dry but isolated light showers
OL,7,Fpossible. Some hazy sunnier spells
OL,8,Fdeveloping later in the day,
OL,9,Fespecially for Dumfries and Galloway,
OL,10,Fwinds remaining light.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA mainly dry and bright
OL,13,Fevening with some late hazy sunshine.
OL,14,FThe rest of the night will remain dry
OL,15,Ffor most, but the odd shower possible
OL,16,Fin the west later.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FA dry and bright start to the
OL,19,Fday with patchy cloud. Showers will
OL,20,Fdevelop for the afternoon, some of
OL,21,Fwhich may be heavy and thundery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
